      "content": "Here is a draft for your rejection email. It's important to be genuine while remaining professional, which is why I've focused on acknowledging his strengths. You can tell Marcus that while his technical skills were impressive, the final decision leaned toward a candidate whose background more closely matched your immediate needs with the cloud architecture. This keeps the focus on the specific requirements rather than questioning his overall talent.",
