    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's better. i think i'll use that. actually, could you also give me a few tips on how to handle the follow-up if he asks for more detailed feedback? like if he pushes back on the cloud architecture thing and asks for more specifics on what he was missing. how do i stay professional without getting dragged into a long debate?",
